09\u0938\u0915\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Banner Upload<\/mark> \u0915\u0930\u0964 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">App<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Front<\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Show <\/mark>\u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u091c\u093f\u0938 \u0924\u0930\u093e\u0939 \u0938\u0947 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0926\u0941\u0915\u093e\u0928\u094b\u0902 \u0915\u0947 \u092c\u093e\u0939\u0930 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Main Banner<\/mark> \u0926\u0947\u0916\u093e \u0939\u094b\u0917\u093e\u0964 \u092a\u0930 \u0906\u092a \u092f\u0939\u093e banner \u0915\u094b \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u092e\u0928 \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u094b\u0924\u092c\u093f\u0915 \u092c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0930 \u0932\u0917\u093e \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u0914\u0930 \u091c\u092c \u091c\u0939\u0947 \u0909\u0938\u0938\u0947 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Offer <\/mark>\u0915\u0947 \u092e\u094b\u0924\u092c\u093f\u0915 \u092f\u093e<mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> Products<\/mark> \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u094b\u0924\u092c\u093f\u0915 change \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948\u0964 <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"145\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0036-1024x145.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12102\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0036-1024x145.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0036-500x71.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0036-768x109.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0036.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0906\u092a <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#cd3636\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Select Position<\/mark><\/strong> \u092e\u0947\u0902 Click \u0915\u0930 \u0915\u0947 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 Banner \u0915\u094b Choose \u0915\u0930 \u0938\u0915\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 \u0915\u093f \u0906\u092a\u0915\u094b \u0905\u092a\u0928\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Banner Top<\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902 Show \u0915\u0930\u0928\u093e \u0939\u0948\u0964 \u092f\u093e <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f58722\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Bottom<\/mark> \u092e\u0947\u0902\u0964 <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0032-1024x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-12103 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0032-1024x533.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0032-500x260.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0032-768x400.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.kalamacademy.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/IMG-20240323-WA0032.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\n<ol>\n<li>\u091c\u092c \u0906\u092a Top \u092e\u0947\u0902 click \u0915\u0930\u0924\u0947 \u0939\u0948 \u0924\u094b \u09